{"tid":1628938,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"10 月 4 日觀塘站，係被popo自己縱火","createTime":"2019-10-06T05:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T09:47:58.000Z","uid":291947,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b14d858f7c05e608923dc919fa7a037a40213357","tid":1628938,"uid":291947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:31:27.000Z","msg":"10 月 4 日觀塘站，係被popo自己縱火時序分析：<br />\n<br />\n7:50 立場新聞 live 影到示威者破壞完再逃走，返轉頭再影站內情況，服務站依然完好,之前示威者只是敲爛東西，完全無用火的東西，甚至有用消防喉射水意圖破壞電子設施，效果是更難起火。<br />\n<br />\n9:00 有市民影到觀塘站已經有防暴<br />\n10:17 地鐵宣布關站<br />\n<br />\n10:30 消防正在撲火<br />\n<br />\n次日港鐵全日罷駛，向外公布車站損毀情況<br />\n<br />\n觀塘站的圖片如同災難過後，情況嚴重<br />\n<br />\n（Form Facebook 香港突發事故報料區)<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2306067772853755/https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2306067772853755/https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2306067772853755/https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2306067772853755/https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2306067772853755/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2306067772853755%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2306067772853755%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2306067772853755%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2306067772853755%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2306067772853755%2F&d=15TDSCYqMG0%2FxcOE0oxfEProWj9UcGxh4mdojqPZn1M%3D&h=066dc506\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2306067772853755/https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2306067772853755/https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2306067772853755/https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2306067772853755/https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2306067772853755/</a><br />\n<br />\n至於誰令這火光四起？示威者有冇可能係落閘後又有防暴在場情況下縱火？<br />\n<br />\n另外補充分析點解係觀塘容易嫁禍，當時無其他記者在採訪觀塘站因為無預告嘢會發生，立場的記者只是趕去採訪突發的民間記者會，經過觀塘站撞破事件採訪到，到立場的記者影到防暴已到駐守，示威者都一早離開，就結束了 live，所以個&ldquo;被安排&ldquo;的大火才在防暴進駐之後無記者的情況下發生。<br />\n<br />\n請公開觀塘站閉路電視片段 !"},{"pid":"2463515a605d2ca35ac07b949026f62b24acbc38","tid":1628938,"uid":310554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:33:01.000Z","msg":"推爆佢呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a3a1d9da4b92a38d8c816cb4db51b4c7d3b1a5","tid":1628938,"uid":291947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:33:47.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"0eeae36c84bf7731d4f70282a6d9d2f127118242","tid":1628938,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:34:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1400 九龍梳士巴利花園<br />\n1400 港島銅鑼灣SOGO</span></span>"},{"pid":"9e7137d55cbc11c319f45ce4837da7bfbf260273","tid":1628938,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:36:38.000Z","msg":"搜集罪證呀<br />\n<br />\n【行動】盡快整理所有警暴片段，同納粹暴行做對比，爭取西方實際行動支持香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請幫手推文支持<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"319dbcadc21f94ea39ef3f40503e8c71c0d9639b","tid":1628938,"uid":291947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:42:33.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"9d28827a28cb25abb23ffeb5281a8e9c14abe3a2","tid":1628938,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:50:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反緊急法！反獨裁特首</span><br />\nSignature簽名檔：保衛家園，對抗極權<br />\n「反極權運動」守護香港，深層改革<br />\n<br />\n裝修裝飾要小心，最好貼返張紙！<br />\n威力愈強嘅